<p style="text-align: center;">本文系<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yuannn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6062512); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6062512&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1601863228" alt="YUANNN" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6062512)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yuannn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6062512); return false;">YUANNN</a></span>的外围作品</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/yuannn">点击此处查看该作者的更多作品</a></p>
<hr />
<p style="text-align: center;">——关于“存在即合理”的一些小思考，或者说是云南民歌《一窝雀》的音觉</p>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="credit-back" style="text-align: center;">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/2" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="height:2em;width: 100%;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
